summary: Some mesh I made as unfinished armour.
descriptionHtml:
It's not at all lore friendly but I tried to make it a bit lore friendly. My idea of this "Armour" is that it generates a protective field but using the energy generated inside of the body. It's has bits of gold to resemble Dwemer materials and the grey to resemble steel and the dark red padding to resemble leather.

Note that if you do use this for anything tell me. Also I don't need credit.
author: Tazmai
